<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <% provide(:title, "Projects") %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag('static_pages_js') %>
</head>
<body id="education">
  <div id="titleDiv">
    <p>
      Curious about what I've been tinkering with in my spare time? Check out the projects below!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="panel-container" class="container">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-body projectPanel">
        <h4 class="projectHeader">HitMeUp
          <a href="http://sudowoodo-hitmeup.herokuapp.com"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
        </h4>
        <div class="projectBody">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-info projectBtn">See the Tech</button>
          <div id="projectText" class="projectInfo">
            <p class="infoP">
              Having trouble organizing those huge social outings and family reunions or just want to see who's
              free for some quick lunch? HitMeUp allows you to maintain a calendar of your personal events and
              compares them to those in your friends list to find optimal free time! Check out your friends tab
              to get a quick checkup on who's free at the moment or visit their profile page to see their
              extensive calendar. Don't worry about privacy issues, HitMeUp automatically omits your calendar from
              your profile page to those who aren't on your friends list!
            </p>
            <p class="techP collapse">
              Web Framework: Django<br><br>
              Front-end: HTML/SCSS, Jinja, ReactJS, Javascript, Bootstrap<br><br>
              Back-end: Python, PostgreSQL<br><br>
              Misc: Git, PyCharm
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="projectImg">
            <img alt="HitMeUpPic" src="assets/HitMeUp.jpg"/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="panel-container" class="container">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-body projectPanel">
        <h4 class="projectHeader">My Personal Site</h4>
        <div class="projectBody">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-info projectBtn">See the Tech</button>
          <div id="projectText" class="projectInfo">
            <p class="infoP">
              My personal website for employment and resume purposes ( you're on it right now! ).
              Feel free to browse the site for information about me or to find extra info on things
              I put on my resume!
            </p>
            <p class="techP collapse">
              Web Framework: Ruby on Rails<br><br>
              Front-end: HTML/SCSS, Javascript, JQuery, Bootstrap<br><br>
              Back-end: Ruby<br><br>
              Misc: Git, Rubymine
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="projectImg">
            <img alt="TODO PIC" src=""/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>